" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"e.fundamentals logo\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" />      </div>\n      <div class=\"brd_testimonial_item_content\">\n                    <div class=\"brd_testimonial_item_excerpt\">\n              The self-management aspect of Bright Data’s platform is great, and the customer service is absolutely outstanding.            </div>\n                  </div>\n      <a href=\"https://brightdata.com/testimonials/efundamentals\" class=\"brd_testimonial_item_rm\">\n        Read more        <svg class=\"cta_ic\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\">\n          <g fill-rule=\"evenodd\">\n            <path class=\"cta_ic-line_path\" d=\"M0 5h7\"\n              data-uw-styling-context=\"true\"></path>\n            <path class=\"cta_ic-tip_path\" d=\"M1 1l4 4-4 4\"\n              data-uw-styling-context=\"true\"></path>\n          </g>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"brd_testimonial_item\">\n  <div class=\"brd_testimonial_item_inner\">\n    <div class=\"brd_testimonial_item_col brd_testimonial_item_col_33\">\n            <div class=\"author_img\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://brightdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Donat-Borsodi_GreyMatter.png\" class=\"brd_post_thumbnail_img wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://brightdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Donat-Borsodi_GreyMatter.png 800w, https://brightdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Donat-Borsodi_GreyMatter-50x50.png 50w, https://brightdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Donat-Borsodi_GreyMatter-768x768.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" />        <div class=\"hes_video\">\n                    </div>\n      </div>\n                <div class=\"author_name\">Donát Borsódi</div>\n      <div class=\"author_title\">Founder and CEO at GreyMatter Ltd.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"brd_testimonial_item_col brd_testimonial_item_col_66\">\n      <div class=\"brd_test